										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img loading="lazy" class=" wp-image-223312 alignleft" src="https://coscharisgroup.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/8650EA71-69B1-45FB-9E88-9C0B911467AB-576x1024.jpg" alt="" width="141" height="250" srcset="https://coscharisgroup.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/8650EA71-69B1-45FB-9E88-9C0B911467AB-576x1024.jpg 576w, https://coscharisgroup.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/8650EA71-69B1-45FB-9E88-9C0B911467AB-169x300.jpg 169w, https://coscharisgroup.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/8650EA71-69B1-45FB-9E88-9C0B911467AB-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://coscharisgroup.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/8650EA71-69B1-45FB-9E88-9C0B911467AB.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 141px) 100vw, 141px" />With gratitude to the Almighty God and total submission to His will, the board and the entire Executive team of Coscharis Group hereby announce the sudden death of our Vice – President, Mrs. Charity Maduka. She died peacefully in her family home in Nnewi, Anambra State, Nigeria on the evening of Saturday 27 November, 2021. She was born on January 15, 1958.</p>
