		<title>COSCHARIS MOTORS EXCITES FORD CUSTOMERS WITH FREE SERVICE PACK</title>
		<link>https://coscharisgroup.net/coscharis-motors-excites-ford-customers-with-free-service-pack</link>
					<comments>https://coscharisgroup.net/coscharis-motors-excites-ford-customers-with-free-service-pack#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[coscharis_admin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 25 Sep 2020 19:08:23 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[news]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://coscharisgroup.net/?p=213008</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[&#160; Coscharis&#160;Motors Plc, a foremost automobile dealer and sole distributor of Ford vehicles in Nigeria is offering free service to her customers who purchase&#160;a brand new Ford car.&#160;Although, itself still reeling from the effect of the global economic doldrums caused by the Covid-19 pandemic, Coscharis Motors Plc still finds it expedient to support her Ford [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter  wp-image-213009" src="https://coscharisgroup.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Ford-Strip1-1024x239.png" alt="" width="898" height="209" srcset="https://coscharisgroup.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Ford-Strip1-1024x239.png 1024w, https://coscharisgroup.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Ford-Strip1-300x70.png 300w, https://coscharisgroup.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Ford-Strip1-768x179.png 768w, https://coscharisgroup.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Ford-Strip1.png 1915w" sizes="(max-width: 898px) 100vw, 898px" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Coscharis&nbsp;</span>Motors Plc, a foremost automobile dealer and sole distributor of Ford vehicles in Nigeria is offering free service to her customers who purchase&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: 400;">a brand new Ford car.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Although, itself still reeling from the effect of the global economic doldrums caused by the Covid-19 pandemic, Coscharis Motors Plc still finds it expedient to support her Ford customers in their drive towards navigating out of the economic recession. This, the auto dealer hopes to achieve through her Free Service Pack offer. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Announcing the offer, Felix Mahan who is the Brand Manager, Ford, at Coscharis Motors said, “This is our token to support our teaming Ford customers by minimizing</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" class="wp-image-213010 aligncenter" src="https://coscharisgroup.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Ford-Strip2-1024x461.png" alt="" width="785" height="353" srcset="https://coscharisgroup.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Ford-Strip2-1024x461.png 1024w, https://coscharisgroup.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Ford-Strip2-300x135.png 300w, https://coscharisgroup.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Ford-Strip2-768x346.png 768w, https://coscharisgroup.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Ford-Strip2.png 1489w" sizes="(max-width: 785px) 100vw, 785px" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&nbsp;the cost of vehicle ownership for those who have refused to buckle under the weight of the global economic recession, occasioned by the Covid-19 pandemic, but have resolved to go further and vie for opportunities to help pull their businesses and by extension our nation, out of the proverbial economic woods.”</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The free service offer is available at all Coscharis Motors Plc showrooms and offices spread throughout the country and all Quick Lane centers alike. The promo which started on September 1</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">st</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> is valid till December 31</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">st</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> 2020. Any customer who purchases a brand new Ford car from Coscharis Motors during the promo period gets a free service pack which covers vehicle service parts and labour, for 12 months or 16,000 kilometers, whichever comes first.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Mahan further said, “At Coscharis Motors, we don’t just sell the car, we back it up with world class after-sales service. All our service centers are manned by certified professional technicians equipped with latest tools and using only genuine OEM parts and lubricants. These are the people who will administer this free service offer and other services as required by our valued customers, to keep their vehicle working optimally throughout its life span.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This is not the first time that Coscharis is supporting her new car customers with free after-sales services. Recall that in the recent past, Coscharis offered her customers a free service pack called Extended Service Plan (ESP) which offered free service for four years or 120,000km. The ESP helped many Ford owners to drastically minimize the cost of ownership of their Ford cars in those days. </span></p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
